# LaTeX Tables Directory

**Auto-generated files - do not edit manually!**

## Purpose

These LaTeX files are automatically generated from CSV files in `tables/csv/` using the conversion script.

## Workflow

1. Edit CSV files in `tables/csv/`
2. Run conversion: `python scripts/csv_to_latex.py --all`
3. These `.tex` files are generated automatically
4. Main LaTeX document includes these files via `\input{}` commands

## Regenerating

To regenerate all LaTeX files from CSV:
```bash
python scripts/csv_to_latex.py --all
```

**Do not edit these files manually** - your changes will be overwritten when you run the conversion script.
